A Pilot Clinical Study on the Prognostic Relevance of Plasmatic Exosomes Levels 
in Oral Squamous Cell Carcinoma Patients.

Rodríguez Zorrilla S(1), Pérez-Sayans M(2)(3), Fais S(4), Logozzi M(5), Gallas 
Torreira M(6), García García A(7)(8).

Author information:
(1)Oral Medicine, Oral Surgery and Implantology Unit, School of Medicine and 
